download sublimetext editor
xampp apacher server
download and install node.js
npm install -g sass command on cli
npm install -g grunt-cli command on cli
npm install grunt-cli --save-dev command on cli
creating package.json, Gruntfile.js
npm install command on cli


react app steps-
1. download and install node.js
2. npm create-react-app apna-section
3. cd apna-section npm install
4. modify package.json and create webpack.config.js
5. npm install webpack webpack-cli
5. npm install sass-loader style-loader html-loader css-loader webpack-dev-server --save-dev command on cli

server setup-
1. npm init
2. npm i express cors mongoose body-parser --save
3. npm i nodemon --save
4. download and install mongodb community server, mongodb compass
5. Do changes in package.json, index.js of server, functioncomponent.js of client


